呵，抱歉抱歉。\n不过小麻里奈非常有干劲呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event289-01-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"所有的工作人员都是这样啦。\n毕竟这是CiRCLE和RiNG联合举办的\n户外摇滚音乐节啊！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event289-01-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":225}],"windowDisplayName":"凛凛子","body":"这倒也是呢！\n符合『遇见乐队，与乐队共度青春』这个主题的乐队\n都聚集在了一起","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":225,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":225,"voiceId":"event289-01-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"是啊。虽然从企划到现在花了很长时间，\n但是我们已经做好了万全的准备，会让所有到场的观众开心","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"event289-01-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"不过……其实昨晚我太兴奋